resources.string: 5G Enhanced Call refers to a series of services that enhance system capabilities and enable service innovation based on the operator\'s IMS network, which improve the user experience for both individual and enterprise users. The most notable technical feature is the addition of a data channel and AR technology on top of the existing IMS audio and video channels, and it relies on the IMS DC SDK on the device, enabling interactive information exchange during calls and upgrading the user experience.\nUsing enhanced call features requires the \"Display over other apps\" and \"Read call log\" permissions.
